ul.li: Each service gets it's own database
trpc used for communication between services in the backend
Kafka is used for event streaming
Backend services are either ExpressJS or NestJS
Each service in the Backend owns a Queue and a Database
Frontend services are written in NextJS
The backend sends events to Either Kafka or the event bus (Publish / Subscribe)
Sytem cache is provided by a redis cluster
